Bitcoin Server (bs) is a console application that is included as part of [[libbitcoin-server|Libbitcoin_Server]]. It implements a full node on the Bitcoin P2P network as well as a blockchain query interface based on [ZeroMQ](http://zeromq.org). Bitcoin Server is a major update to [[Obelisk]].

